    "num": "12",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">12</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Reflection</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Considering Texican Identity Today</h2><ul><li>Texican heritage influences modern Texas culture</li><li>Understanding origins helps appreciate cultural diversity</li><li>Reflect on how historical identities persist or change</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Reflecting on Texican origins allows learners to connect historical identities to contemporary cultural expressions and appreciate the ongoing influence of indigenous and Hispanic heritage in Texas. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s2\">[2]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s4\">[4]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s7\">[7]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Modern celebrations of Texican heritage include festivals, language preservation, and cultural education.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Reflect on how learning about Texican origins changes your view of Texas culture.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Avoid viewing historical identities as irrelevant to modern cultural dynamics.</p></div></div>",
