    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">42</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Source Analysis Practice</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Interpreting a Texican Letter Excerpt</h2><ul><li>Identify key themes in the letter.</li><li>Note language reflecting cultural identity.</li><li>Consider the letter’s historical context.</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Analyzing a letter excerpt helps learners practice extracting historical information and understanding Texican perspectives. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s11\">[11]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> A letter mentioning land disputes and family ties illustrates frontier challenges and social networks.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> What does this letter reveal about Texican life and identity?</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Avoid ignoring subtle cultural cues in the language.</p></div></div>",
