    "eyebrow": "Reflection and Application",
    "num": "48",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">48</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Reflection and Application</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Reflecting on the Texican Historical Experience</h2><ul><li>Primary sources deepen understanding of Texican culture.</li><li>Historical reconstruction requires critical analysis.</li><li>Texican identity is complex and multifaceted.</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Reflecting on the use of primary sources and contested interpretations prepares learners to appreciate the richness and challenges of Texican history. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s10\">[10]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s11\">[11]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s16\">[16]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Synthesizing letters, documents, and artifacts reveals a Texican identity shaped by cultural blending and political complexity.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Write a brief reflection on how primary sources changed your understanding of Texicans.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Avoid simplistic or one-dimensional views of Texican history.</p></div></div>",
